snippet.textDisplay: This song is a tribute to women of all ages. Women do so much to try to fit the expectations of others, starting with body image. But this empowering song affirms that you are enough, plain and simple, just the way you are. You don't have to try so hard. You just have to accept yourself. Women occupy many roles, and this song playfully celebrates all of them, from sweet to sassy to seductress, from mom to mean to everything in between.
